<p>
  <span class="nym">Bert</span>
  <span class="gen">m.</span>
  
  <span class="etym"><span class="lang">Old High German</span> <i>beraht</i>, <span class="lang">Old Saxon</span> <i>berht</i> 'bright' from <span class="lang">Proto-Germanic</span> <i>*berhtaz</i> used as a standalone name, or a diminutive of any of various names using this element as a prototheme or deuterotheme.
</span>
  
</p>
  
  
  


